{"tid":1180910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"6月9號遊行詳情?","createTime":"2019-06-01T07:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T11:35:03.000Z","uid":207653,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6a0d423ff1a8cafb503e6d4ebc3f10892d9d0f","tid":1180910,"uid":207653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"睇咗咁耐都唔覺啲咩真係好實質嘅指示<br />\n感覺係大家都好有火<br />\n但係團火唔知要燒去邊個方向咁<br />\n剩係知9號2點半要去銅鑼灣<br />\n遊行要做啲咩?要準備banner?有冇口號?<br />\n<br />\n啱先上網search過<br />\n民陣有向警方爭取遊行路線乜乜乜<br />\n但係好似冇啲咩行動大綱咁<br />\n其實如果冇detail嘅話<br />\n不如係到討論下當日可以做啲咩<br />\n比大家都有個底<br />\n有多啲資訊先會有更多嘅人選擇加入<br />\n或者呼籲下民陣講下少少資料<br />\n唔好比人覺得係出去行個圈唱下歌就完咁<br />\n<br />\n補充翻: <br />\n唔好覺得係到討論行動會比警察知<br />\n其實寧願比警察知都唔好唔比料啲遊行人士<br />\n遲啲出到去大家都一盤散沙咁<br />\n啲凝聚力行動力就會冇曬<br />\n遊行嘅效果就會大打折扣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=c6138461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a>"},{"pid":"5ce0a45cf23651f2364c238df5e2384a71fb4017","tid":1180910,"uid":207653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2707db3113ad7a896eb4cb4be87e7c3033fa3e","tid":1180910,"uid":180895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"其實我都想知多啲詳情"},{"pid":"3fbf418a0aa159dac3019d5c4d3279c78c736c7d","tid":1180910,"uid":207653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd2707db3113ad7a896eb4cb4be87e7c3033fa3e","tid":1180910,"uid":180895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"其實我都想知多啲詳情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"驚到時會好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}